name: "Her Shoe Game Sick" black cotton legging
description:
The 1st design in our legging's collection for women. With such a popular demand for female apparel, we bring to you our legging's collection, designed exclusively by the co-owner, Aimee. Leggings are such a staple item in any female's wardrobe, whether they are dressed up or dressed down. We took the "Her Shoe Game Sick" t-shirt design and placed it in an iconic spot on the leggings. We wanted the design to be seen on "on feet" pictures that are being taken in many shapes and forms in social media (i.e. Instagram) 

Leggings are 100% cotton and print is vinyl. Orders will be shipped with washing/care instructions. 

**Sizing Chart:
Small: 2-4
Medium: 6-8
Large: 10-12
X-large: 12-14

LIMITED QUANTITY AVAILABLE!
